* Repository\nOrganization
** .gitignore
***_ Exclude temp outputs
***_ Exclude credentials
***_ Explicit removal for tracked files
** Folder Structure
***_ Group related notebooks/files
***_ Logical depth hierarchy
** Branch Hygiene
***_ Remove stale branches after merge
***_ Local branches: persist 30 days
** Size Limits
***_ Working branch: max 1 GB
***_ Max 20,000 assets
***_ Sparse checkout for large repos
@endmindmap
